uk.ac.ucl.cs.gc01.restaurant_billing_system.objects

  • Packages that use uk.ac.ucl.cs.gc01.restaurant_billing_system.objects 
    Package Description
    uk.ac.ucl.cs.gc01.restaurant_billing_system.app
    Provides the classes necessary to create an applet and the classes an applet uses to navigate the GUI.
    uk.ac.ucl.cs.gc01.restaurant_billing_system.database_management
    Provides the classes necessary to query the database in order to manipulate elements in the database.
    uk.ac.ucl.cs.gc01.restaurant_billing_system.gui_testers
    Package contains deprecated GUI testers
    uk.ac.ucl.cs.gc01.restaurant_billing_system.objects
    Provides the classes necessary to represent the different objects that form the restaurant in order to build the system.
  • Classes in uk.ac.ucl.cs.gc01.restaurant_billing_system.objects used by uk.ac.ucl.cs.gc01.restaurant_billing_system.app 
    Class and Description
    DigitalClock
    The DigitalClock class generates a Label which displays a live clock.
    Employee
    The Employee class used to generate the employees for our restaurant It provides a template for the Manager class.
    FoodItem
    The FoodItem class represents the different FoodItems on the menu.
    OrderDetails
    The OrderDetails class represents the different details contained in an order.
    OrderItems
    The OrderItems class represents the different details contained in an order as well as the details about the items in those orders.
    Table
    The Table class represents the different details that a Table can store.
